headline: Toll Brothers (TOL) Surpasses Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Toll Brothers (TOL) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 22.38% and 9.54%, respectively, for the quarter ended April 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
